game.name: Rapunzel Wedding Party Dress
game.description:
Your beloved princess Rapunzel has chosen her love to get married. Yes, she is going to marry with a handsome Flynn today and a big wedding party would be held in the evening. Two of her best friends Ariel and Aurora have been invited as the bridesmaids by Rapunzel. All the preparation for the wedding has been done except the selection of the nice outfits for the groom and bride. They both now need your help for this purpose. Do you give your helping hands to them now? Join Rapunzel Wedding Party Dress and be prepared to have a fantastic wedding!

It is a big day in the life of this beautiful couple, so they do not want to compromise on the selection of their outfits. Give Flynn a perfect suit with a matching shirt and a pair of shoes in this brand new dressing game for girls! Make sure to provide him with a lovely hairstyle before finalizing his look. Now dress up Rapunzel, who is waiting for her turn. Give your girl a wonderful hairstyle, a fabulous white color gown and combine her dress with a pair of awesome shoes! 

Do not forget to decorate her head with a fine crown and give her hands a bouquet of flowers. Your cool fashion abilities will surely guide you to pick out the right dresses for both of them. Try to give a heart shaped balloon written “I Love You” on it to the hands of Flynn to show off his true love feelings! Good luck to make some needful suggestions about what the groom and bride should put on to look fabulous in our princess wedding game!
